quran[10{c,v,t}:
12,5,"jawab mein is ke baap ne kaha,"" beta, apna yeh khawab apne bhaiyon ko nah sunana warna woh tairay darpay azaar ho jayen ge, haqeeqat yeh hai ke shetan aadmi ka khula dushman hai"
12,6,"aur aisa hi hoga ( jaissa to ne khawab mein dekha hai ke ) tera rab tujhe ( apne kaam ke liye ) muntakhib kere ga aur tujhe baton ki teh taq pohanchna sikhayiye ga aur tairay oopar aur all yaqoob par apni Nemat isi terhan poori kere ga jis terhan is se pehlay woh tairay buzurgon, ibrahim aur ishaq par kar chuka hai, yaqeenan tera rab Aleem aur hakeem hai """
12,7,haqeeqat yeh hai ke yousuf aur is ke bhaiyon ke qissa mein inn poochnay walon ke liye barri nishanain hain
12,8,"yeh qissa yun shuru hota hai ke is ke bhaiyon ne aapas mein kaha"" yeh yousuf aur is ka bhai, dono hamaray waalid ko hum sab se ziyada mehboob hain halaank hum aik poora jatha hain sachhi baat yeh hai ke hamaray abba jaan ba lkl hi behak gay hain"
12,9,"chalo yousuf ko qatal kar do ya usay kahin pheink do taakay tumahray waalid ki tavajja sirf tumhari hi taraf ho jaye yeh kaam kar lainay ke baad phir naik ban rehna """
12,10,"is par un mein se aik bola"" yousuf ko qatal nah karo, agar kuch karna hi hai to usay kisi andhay kunvey mein daal do koi aata jata qaafla usay nikaal le jaye ga """
12,11,"is qarardad par unhon ne ja kar apne baap se kaha"" abba jaan, kya baat hai ke aap yousuf ke maamla mein hum par bharosa nahi karte halaank hum is ke sachey kher khuwa hain ?"
12,12,"kal usay hamaray sath bhaij dijiya ga kuch churcug le ga aur khail kood se bhi dil behlaye ga hum is ki hifazat ko mojood hain """
12,13,"baap ne kaha"" tumhara usay le jana mujhe shaq guzarta hai aur mujh ko andesha hai ke kahin usay bheria nah phaar kha ye jabkay tum is se ghaafil ho """
12,14,"unhon ne jawab diya"" agar hamaray hotay usay bhir yai ne kha liya, jabkay hum aik jatha hain, tab to hum barray hi nikammay hon ge """
